
Create a DB User for API

sql
CopyEdit
CREATE USER 'jenkins_user'@'%' IDENTIFIED BY 'your_strong_password';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON jenkins_pipeline_db.* TO 'jenkins_user'@'%';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
EXIT;
Allow External Connections (Optional)
Edit MySQL config:
sudo nano /etc/mysql/mysql.conf.d/mysqld.cnf
Change:
bind-address = 127.0.0.1
to:
bind-address = 0.0.0.0
Then: